name: Just Hanging out ...Doing Magic.
description:
The friendship between Skully B. and Aughostus is not a boring one. Whether they're making music, making magic or just hanging out... it's always a good time! Mixed media original painting on birch panel - this version has slight digital enhancements i.e. the signature in the bottom left corner.

2560 px x 2000 px at 300 dpi
